// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1277 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 6b14acd8-2253-5b2e-9a65-025955438910

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*")
